  <div class="mb-2 body-sm text-grey-5C"><div class="metafield-rich_text_field"><p>For external use only • Do not use on damaged or broken skin • Stop use and ask a doctor if rash occurs • When using this product keep out of eyes • Rinse with water to remove • Keep out of reach of children • If swallowed, get medical help or contact a Poison Control Center right away</p></div></div>
</details>

